snippet.textDisplay:
Here is my decade so 2011 best head teacher at my school left and got a short term Terrible replacement. Started to make peace with bully 1, 2012 free from the rain of terror of bully 1 and got the right sen support for my disabilities, 2013 finally have coping mechanisms for my disabilities, new school, met bully 2, 2014, got a new baby sister (only other sibling) started migration along the curvy path, got my first unofficial/secret boyfriend Jacob who I disguised behind a fake girlfriend willow, 2015, started coming out of the closet to people who I don’t know well as if everything goes tits up I probably won’t see again met a supportive scout leader who unknowingly added in that support. Thank you ash. Got revenge on bully 2 with a yogurt head insedent, 2016, when I opened up to close friends about my sexuality, lost a few of my friends who where not supportive. fractured my collar bone, 2017 got an internet pen pall but only lasted a month bully 2 got expelled and I brand in a tub of celebration got moved up a band at school, 2018 got selected for the world scout jamboree had a crunch on a guy in class who was straight but interested in the gay community complete GCSEs and picked alevels, 2019, met new Frends lost touch with a lot of old ones, hit the bump in the road of a Levels got my first above bored job, got drunk for the first time and got conditional offers for uni, as well as my 2nd major injury (soft tissue damage to my ankle),

If you can identify me from this please do not comment down below but if you want to discuss use alternative means of communication, if not ask away,

snippet.textDisplay:
12/31/19 is not the end of the decade, 12/31/20 is.

Decades, Centuries, and millennia all start with a year ending with a 1, and end with a years ending with a 0.

There was no year 0, so the first decade was 1-10, first century was 1-100, and first millennium was 1-1000.

Note, 1999 wasn’t the end of the 20 century, 2000 was.

Research before planning or producing anything. What you think is correct may not be.
